│   GUEST (role = 0)                                              │
│   └── Read-only access                                         │
│   └── Sees leaderboard with USERNAMES only                     │
│   └── Cannot see real names of any student                     │
│                                                                 │
│   ADMIN / EDITOR (role = 1)                                     │
│   └── Full CRUD access                                         │
│   └── Sees leaderboard with USERNAMES                          │
│   └── CAN see real full names of students                      │
│   └── Requires access key to register                          │
│                                                                 │
